description_1: Assessed the efficacy of machine learning models to recapitulate neural cell identity from mRNA expression [1](https://www.pnas.org/doi/10.1073/pnas.1911413116). Investigated the compensatory effects of elevated depolarization on neuronal excitability, conductances, and ion channel mRNA abundances in small neural networks [3](https://mospace.umsystem.edu/xmlui/handle/10355/85790).
